{"tid":2516056,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"林鄭月娥:不接受有人指香港有「警暴」問題 不接受有人醜化和抹黑警隊","createTime":"2021-05-04T11:33:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T17:08:14.000Z","uid":230530,"like":1,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"911f3d2fc1d3ccb6c83c1c73471787c951df7133","tid":2516056,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T11:33:56.000Z","msg":"香港行政長官林鄭月娥出席立法會答問大會表示，不接受有人形容香港處理社會動盪過程中有出現所謂的「警暴」問題。她強調，香港警隊多年以來夜以繼日維持治安，如果無人犯法，警察根本不需要執法。<br />\n<br />\n她又指出，見到有人醜化和抹黑警隊，相信目的是要削弱警隊的執法能力，而最喜歡看到這個情況出現的人，就是犯法者，特別是將暴力升級、不斷犯法的人。她呼籲大家支持警方嚴正執法，才可保持香港穩定安全。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥又表示，近期的社會事件已演變為暴力，糾纏下去會令社會內耗，市民受傷，無法令香港走出困局。她希望大家珍惜法治，如果法治精神不保，後果將相當嚴重。"},{"pid":"467ef4d05cd400989a46e407204088792ec391a7","tid":2516056,"uid":89182,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T11:35:45.000Z","msg":"咁應該立埋辱警罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c33109a7435fcb05ee3539159e693f9179a72cc","tid":2516056,"uid":11291,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T11:37:49.000Z","msg":"黑警係「有牌爛仔」呢句說話一早已經有"},{"pid":"39d2c4d77eb681fb59bdb50afba7fa97ee1aaa37","tid":2516056,"uid":14422,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T11:38:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUAjFePu7CeJvuhGQhLyps4TrRJ2CdwCMCnsZR3ke6Aj9?filename=1wWfpOW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1wWfpOW.gif&h=9531b6e7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPNsoTURHcFTxsn8NqbEfm7smnG6XqGgcSUjHUCm8eoQB?filename=acJadHh.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FacJadHh.gif&h=6bc1452d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9aa5d3a8030e0215d5a839e2b3739126d69c2bbf","tid":2516056,"uid":11291,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T11:39:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdgVKNeuw5dNjFWcZJfWwvzbQdRPmj15TXETg4HNJPTon?filename=A4VTbuu.gif\" data-thu